In <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../706/126706.xml">
pattern recognition</link> and <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../488/233488.xml">
machine learning</link>, a <b>feature vector</b> is an n-dimensional <link xlink:type="simple" xlink:href="../533/32533.xml">
vector</link> of numerical <event wordnetid="100029378" confidence="0.8">
